Package de.dedede.model.data.dtos

Class ApplicationDto

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.dedede.model.data.dtos.ApplicationDto
  • public class ApplicationDto
extends java.lang.Object
    This DTO (data transfer object) is responsible for aggregating and encapsulating data about the application for transfer.

    See the ApplicationDao class to which this DTO is passed.

    Author:
    Sergei Pravdin
